P_HTM[104]="*7. Ajjhattāniccātītānāgatasuttaṃ**The Interior as Impermanent in the Three Times*";
P_HTM[105]="*“Cakkhuṃ, bhikkhave, aniccaṃ atītānāgataṃ;**“Mendicants, the eye of the past and future is impermanent,*";
P_HTM[106]="*ko pana vādo paccuppannassa.**let alone the present.*";
