P_HTM[940]="*yampidaṃ manosamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā adukkhamasukhaṃ vā, tampi niccaṃ vā aniccaṃ vā”ti?**The pleasant, painful, or neutral feeling that arises conditioned by mind contact: is that permanent or impermanent?”*";
