P_HTM[3865]="*tatra vo rāgo pahātabbo.* **";
P_HTM[3866]="*Yaṃ, bhikkhave, aniccaṃ, tatra vo rāgo pahātabbo”ti.* **";
P_HTM[3867]="*3. Ajjhattaaniccachandarāgasuttaṃ**Desire and Greed for the Impermanent Interior*";
