P_HTM[3877]="*4-6. Dukkhachandādisuttaṃ**171–173. Dukkhachandādisutta*";
P_HTM[3878]="*“Yaṃ, bhikkhave, dukkhaṃ, tatra vo chando pahātabbo, rāgo pahātabbo, chandarāgo pahātabbo.**“Mendicants, you should give up desire … greed … desire and greed for what is suffering.*";
