P_HTM[3891]="*10-12. Bāhirāniccachandādisuttaṃ**177–179. Bāhirāniccachandādisutta*";
P_HTM[3892]="*“Yaṃ, bhikkhave, aniccaṃ, tatra vo chando pahātabbo, rāgo pahātabbo, chandarāgo pahātabbo.**“Mendicants, you should give up desire … greed … desire and greed for what is impermanent.*";
