P_HTM[3894]="*Rūpā, bhikkhave, aniccā; tatra vo chando pahātabbo, rāgo pahātabbo, chandarāgo pahātabbo.**Sights, sounds, smells, tastes, touches, and thoughts are impermanent …”*";
