P_HTM[6637]="*dibbena āyunā … pe … dibbehi phoṭṭhabbehi.**divine life span, beauty, happiness, glory, sovereignty, sights, sounds, smells, tastes, and touches.*";
P_HTM[6638]="*Sādhu kho, devānaminda, dhamme aveccappasādena samannāgamanaṃ hoti:**It’s good to have experiential confidence in the teaching …*";
P_HTM[6639]="*‘svākkhāto bhagavatā dhammo … pe … paccattaṃ veditabbo viññūhī’ti.* **";
