P_HTM[7736]="*Idha, gāmaṇi, ekacco tapassī lūkhajīvī saddhā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito hoti:**Take a self-mortifier who has gone forth from the lay life to homelessness, thinking:*";
