P_HTM[7739]="*Idha pana, gāmaṇi, ekacco tapassī lūkhajīvī saddhā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito hoti:**Take another self-mortifier who has gone forth from the lay life to homelessness, thinking:*";
